Install on Linux:
=================

dr-tv:
------
find your xbmc addons folder:

	cd  ~/.xbmc/addons

create a symlink to the xbmc-dr-tv folder:

	ln -s <path-to-dr-tv> plugin.video.drtv

Start xbmc and find the plugin under Video -> Addons


dr-radio:
---------
find your xbmc addons folder:

	cd  ~/.xbmc/addons

create a symlink to the xbmc-dr-radio folder:

	ln -s <path-to-dr-radio> script.drradio

Start xbmc and find the plugin under Programs.

**Usage**: Left and right buttons change between radio stations. Up and down shifts between quality (bitrate). 

Install on Mac OS X
===================

The same as Linux, but instead of `~/.xbmc/addons`, use `~/Library/Application Support/XBMC/addons` 